\c 14
\p
\v 1 Mukadzi mumwe nomumwe akachenjera anovaka imba yake; Asi benzi rinoiputsa namaoko aro.
\v 2 Anofamba nokururama kwake, anotya Jehovha; Asi wakatsauka panzira dzake, anomudzidza.
\v 3 Mumuromo webenzi mune shamhu yamanyawi; Asi miromo yavakachenjera inovachengeta.
\v 4 Kana pasina nzombe, chidyiro hachine chiro; Asi zvibereko zvizhinji zvinouya nesimba renzombe.
\v 5 Chapupu, chakatendeka, hachirevi nhema; Asi chapupu chenhema chinobudisa mashoko enhema.
\v 6 Mudadi anotsvaka uchenjeri, asi hahupo; Asi zivo haitani kuwanikwa navane njere.
\v 7 Ibva pamberi pebenzi, nekuti haungawani miromo yezivo kwaari.
\v 8 Uchenjeri hwomunhu akangwara ndiko kunzwisisa nzira yake; Asi hupenzi hwamapenzi hunonyengedzera.
\v 9 Chibayiro chezvivi chamapenzi chinodadira; Asi pakati pavakarurama panokufarirana.
\v 10 moyo mumwe nomumwe unoziva kutambudzika kwawo; Mweni haangagoverani nomufaro wawo.
\v 11 Imba yowakaipa ichaparadzwa; Asi tende rowakarurama richafara zvakanaka.
\v 12 Munhu anoona nzira achiti yakarurama; Asi kuguma kwayo inzira dzorufu.
\v 13 Kunyange munhu angaseka hake, moyo ungava neshungu; Kuguma komufaro ndiko kuchema.
\v 14 Ano moyo, anodzokera shure, achagutiswa nenzira dzake; Asi munhu akanaka achagutiswa nezvinobva maari.
\v 15 Asina mano anotenda mashoko ose; Asi akangwara anongwarira mafambiro ake.
\v 16 Akachenjera anotya zvakashata, achizvinzvenga; Asi benzi rinamanyawi, richizvitenda.
\v 17 Anokurumidza kutsamwa, achaita noupenzi; Uye munhu, anofunga mano akaipa, achavengwa.
\v 18 Vasina mano vanogara nhaka yohupenzi; Asi vakangwara vachadzikwa korona yezivo.
\v 19 Vakashata vanogwadama pamberi pavakanaka; Navakaipa pamasuo avakarurama.
\v 20 Murombo anovengwa kunyange nowokwake; Asi shamwari dzavafumi izhinji.
\v 21 Anoshora wokwake, anotadza; Asi ane tsitsi navarombo, ane mufaro.
\v 22 Ko vanofunga zvakaipa havarashiki here? Asi nyasha nezvokwadi ndezvavanofunga zvakanaka
\v 23 Kubata kose kune batsiro; Asi kungotaura nemiromo kunobereka kushaiwa.
\v 24 Korona yavakachenjera ifuma yavo; Asi upenzi hwamapenzi upenzi zvahwo
\v 25 Chapupu chakatendeka chinoponesa mweya yavanhu; Asi anoreva nhema anonyengedzera.
\v 26 Pakutya Jehovha pane simbiso kwazvo Vana vowakadai vachava noutiziro.
\v 27 Kutya Jehovha itsime roupenyu; Kuti munhu apukunyuke pamisungo yorufu.
\v 28 Ukuru hwamambo hunoonekwa pakuwanda kwavanhu; Asi kuparadzwa kwashe kuri pakushaiwa vanhu.
\v 29 Ano moyo murefu ane njere kwazvo; Asi anokurumidza kutsamwa anowedzera upenzi.
\v 30 moyo wakagadzikana ndihwo upenyu hwomuviri; Asi godo rinoodza mapfupa.
\v 31 Anomanikidza murombo, anozvidza Muiti wake; Asi ane tsitsi nomushaiwi, anomukudza.
\v 32 Akaipa anowiswa pasi mukutadza kwake; Asi akarurama ane tariro pakufa kwake.
\v 33 Uchenjeri hunogara pamoyo weane njere; Asi zviri mukati mamapenzi zvinozikamwa.
\v 34 Kururama kunokurisa rudzi; Asi zvivi zvinonyadzisa kurudzi rupi norupi.
\v 35 Mambo anofarira muranda, anoita nokuchenjera; Asi anonyadzisa achatsamwirwa naye.
